#########Ansible installations in Ubuntu##########
1. using Package (Wget/curl)
2. Using Source code
########Ansible Architecture
                                                                                                          Remote servers
Host Inventory,                       ___________________                                      /
Playbooks,        Command Cente ---> | Ansible Python API| ----SSH---> Internet--> Router --> Switch 
Ansible Config,                      |___________________|                                     \
Core Modules,                                                                                            Remote servers
Custom Modules


Note:::: The remote servers should have Python installed along with a library named simplejson in case you are using Python Version 2.5 or an earlier version.


##################### Explanation for Host Inventory 
a. The host inventory file determines the target machines where these plays will be executed.
 
